snippet.textDisplay:
OK, some were ok-ok types,expected better, something that would have STOOD OUT, and some others MISFITS.Good to see talents are explored like Maithali in the COKE STUDIO reprsenting the cultural part but the rappers using words were "too aggressive,out of way" for mingling along with her's, JUST NOT GOING. EXPECTED BETTER Music arrangement.  It seems to opted to make a catchy Holi song,but majorly electronic fushion doesnt helps, but better RICHNESS in composition with more of raw & holi cultural inclusion of lyrics, sounds used would have been better,frankly. Not like somehow trying to fit non-matured rap in 1:54 is just NOT at all going with SAROD. 
Hopefully to see way more better than this which COKE STUDIO BHARAT stood for,the level is already much way up set by previous seasons composers.
AN IMPORTANT FREE SUGGESTION:   ALWAYS TRY TO MAKE SONGS ONLY KEEPING "GOOD MUSIC" IN MIND(Imean real good stuff-lyrics,compositions,arrangements), WHICH WILL HAVE A HEART&SOUL TO IT AND NOT FOR SOME CATCHY,TRENDY-SOMETHING. THATS IT.
